Dialogue: 1,0:01:18.97,0:01:21.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,太安静了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.97,0:01:21.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's too quiet
Dialogue: 1,0:01:21.40,0:01:24.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这附近有点不对劲
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.40,0:01:24.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Something isn't right around here
Dialogue: 1,0:01:35.28,0:01:36.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,该不会是
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.28,0:01:36.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Could it be?
Dialogue: 1,0:01:36.17,0:01:39.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝今天傍晚不在
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.17,0:01:39.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob is gone for the evening
Dialogue: 1,0:01:40.49,0:01:45.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,敬与你共处的美妙傍晚  公共台
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.49,0:01:42.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Here's to a delightful evening
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.87,0:01:45.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,alone with you, public television
Dialogue: 1,0:01:57.37,0:01:59.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,再来再来
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.37,0:01:59.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Do it again, do it again
Dialogue: 1,0:01:59.05,0:02:00.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.05,0:02:00.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,OK
Dialogue: 1,0:02:08.73,0:02:10.69,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你们两个能不能别吵了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.73,0:02:10.69,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Will you two be quiet?
Dialogue: 1,0:02:10.69,0:02:14.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我还要看公共台呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.69,0:02:14.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm trying to watch public television
Dialogue: 1,0:02:16.70,0:02:18.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,再来再来
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.70,0:02:18.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Do it again, do it again
Dialogue: 1,0:02:18.20,0:02:21.76,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,要是他俩傍晚想害我在家都不得安宁
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.20,0:02:21.76,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,If those two want to ruin my quiet evening at home
Dialogue: 1,0:02:21.76,0:02:24.13,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那可差得远了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.76,0:02:24.13,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,they're gonna have to do better than that
Dialogue: 1,0:02:31.03,0:02:31.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,干嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.03,0:02:31.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 1,0:02:31.86,0:02:33.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.86,0:02:33.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Squidward
Dialogue: 1,0:02:37.51,0:02:39.01,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你们该不会还在吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.51,0:02:39.01,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You're still there, aren't you?
Dialogue: 1,0:02:39.39,0:02:40.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,傍晚好  章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.39,0:02:40.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Good evening, Squidward
Dialogue: 1,0:02:40.77,0:02:42.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,别急
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.77,0:02:42.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Not so fast
Dialogue: 1,0:02:42.65,0:02:46.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你们两个小畜生休想害我傍晚不好过
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.65,0:02:46.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You two little monsters aren't about to ruin my evening
Dialogue: 1,0:02:46.38,0:02:47.78,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们才没要害你不好过
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.38,0:02:47.78,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We're not here to ruin it
Dialogue: 1,0:02:47.78,0:02:50.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们是要让你更好过
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.78,0:02:50.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We're here to enhance it
Dialogue: 1,0:02:50.15,0:02:51.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,对不对啊  派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.15,0:02:51.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Isn't that right, pat?
Dialogue: 1,0:02:51.10,0:02:52.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,对  我们是来
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.10,0:02:52.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yeah, we're here
Dialogue: 1,0:02:53.20,0:02:54.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我章鱼哥都这么努力了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.20,0:02:54.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Can't a hard-working squid
Dialogue: 1,0:02:54.97,0:02:57.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就不能自个看会儿电视吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.97,0:02:57.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,get a little TV time alone?
Dialogue: 1,0:02:59.90,0:03:00.66,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.90,0:03:00.66,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob?
Dialogue: 1,0:03:01.02,0:03:01.56,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.02,0:03:01.56,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Patrick?
Dialogue: 1,0:03:02.95,0:03:04.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,又有什么意义
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.95,0:03:04.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What's the point
Dialogue: 1,0:03:08.48,0:03:09.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,能不能放大声点
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.48,0:03:09.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Could you turn it up?
Dialogue: 1,0:03:12.12,0:03:12.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.12,0:03:12.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Squidward?
Dialogue: 1,0:03:13.02,0:03:14.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,能不能关小声点
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.02,0:03:14.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Could you turn it down a little?
Dialogue: 1,0:03:14.32,0:03:16.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,章鱼哥  这是演什么的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.32,0:03:16.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Squidward, what's this about?
Dialogue: 1,0:03:16.70,0:03:18.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,章鱼哥  他怎么这么有感染力
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.70,0:03:18.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Squidward, how come he's so emotional?
Dialogue: 1,0:03:18.92,0:03:20.01,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他是不是反派
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.92,0:03:20.01,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Is he the bad guy?
Dialogue: 1,0:03:20.42,0:03:21.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.42,0:03:21.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Squidward?
Dialogue: 1,0:03:21.05,0:03:21.73,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.05,0:03:21.73,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Squidward?
Dialogue: 1,0:03:21.73,0:03:22.21,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.73,0:03:22.21,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Squidward?
Dialogue: 1,0:03:22.21,0:03:22.73,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.21,0:03:22.73,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Squidward?
Dialogue: 1,0:03:22.73,0:03:23.16,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.73,0:03:23.16,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Squidward?
Dialogue: 1,0:03:23.16,0:03:23.59,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.16,0:03:23.59,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Squidward?
Dialogue: 1,0:03:23.59,0:03:23.99,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.59,0:03:23.99,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Squidward?
Dialogue: 1,0:03:25.74,0:03:26.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,够了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.74,0:03:26.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's it
Dialogue: 1,0:03:26.92,0:03:31.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我只想看公共台放的轻柔爵士
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.92,0:03:28.43,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,All I wanted to do
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.43,0:03:31.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,was watch some smooth jazz on public television
Dialogue: 1,0:03:31.57,0:03:34.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,然而很明显  根本就看不了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.57,0:03:34.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But apparently, that's not gonna happen
Dialogue: 1,0:03:34.52,0:03:38.34,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我又得离开我自己的家
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.52,0:03:38.34,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Once again, I'm going to have to leave my own home
Dialogue: 1,0:03:38.34,0:03:40.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,图个安宁了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.34,0:03:40.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,just to get some peace and quiet
Dialogue: 1,0:03:41.08,0:03:43.36,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好好看我家电视去
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.08,0:03:43.36,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Enjoy my TV
Dialogue: 1,0:03:45.20,0:03:47.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,等下  这我好像看过
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.20,0:03:47.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Wait, I think I've seen this before
Dialogue: 1,0:03:47.37,0:03:48.66,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这段可搞笑了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.37,0:03:48.66,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This part's funny
Dialogue: 1,0:03:48.66,0:03:51.04,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我打算去个遥远的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.66,0:03:51.04,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna go somewhere far away
Dialogue: 1,0:03:51.04,0:03:53.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,远离那两个家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.04,0:03:53.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Somewhere far away from those two
Dialogue: 1,0:03:53.17,0:03:56.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,用我电视看公共台的那两个家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.17,0:03:56.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Watching public television on my TV
Dialogue: 1,0:03:58.80,0:04:00.23,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他们不可能懂真正的文化
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.80,0:04:00.23,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,They wouldn't know real culture
Dialogue: 1,0:04:00.23,0:04:02.98,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就算它像载满水泥的卡车撞过来也一样
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.23,0:04:02.98,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,even if it hit them like a truck full of cement
Dialogue: 1,0:04:30.52,0:04:32.53,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,应该是第五天吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.52,0:04:32.53,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Day five, I think
Dialogue: 1,0:04:32.87,0:04:34.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我在田野之上摇摆而行
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.87,0:04:34.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I've been waddling these fields
Dialogue: 1,0:04:34.95,0:04:37.63,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,又饿又累  还迷了路
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.95,0:04:37.63,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm hungry, tired, and lost
Dialogue: 1,0:04:38.37,0:04:41.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,唯一的优点就是  没有海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.37,0:04:41.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The only good thing about this is, no SpongeBob
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.88,0:04:44.55,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(906,626)}水母田
Dialogue: 1,0:04:43.01,0:04:44.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,水母田
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.01,0:04:44.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Jellyfish fields
Dialogue: 1,0:04:48.96,0:04:50.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那是什么怪东西  派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.96,0:04:50.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What is that thing, Patrick?
Dialogue: 1,0:04:50.87,0:04:51.71,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.87,0:04:51.71,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I don't know
Dialogue: 1,0:04:52.08,0:04:53.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,过去看一下
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.08,0:04:53.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Let's get a closer look
Dialogue: 1,0:04:54.95,0:04:56.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,嗨  陌生人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.95,0:04:56.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hi, stranger
Dialogue: 1,0:04:56.15,0:04:57.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我是海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.15,0:04:57.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I am SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:05:08.47,0:05:09.91,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.47,0:05:09.91,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Wait a minute
Dialogue: 1,0:05:09.91,0:05:11.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他可能不是怪物
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.91,0:05:11.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Maybe he's not a monster
Dialogue: 1,0:05:11.90,0:05:14.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,应该是只濒危物种
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.90,0:05:14.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Maybe he's an endangered species
Dialogue: 1,0:05:14.97,0:05:16.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,应该要救助他
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.97,0:05:16.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We should help him
Dialogue: 1,0:05:16.70,0:05:18.24,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,对  救助他
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.70,0:05:18.24,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yeah, help him
Dialogue: 1,0:05:18.24,0:05:19.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,滚开
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.24,0:05:19.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Go away
Dialogue: 1,0:05:19.27,0:05:21.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,看不出来没人要你吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.27,0:05:21.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Can't you tell nobody wants you?
Dialogue: 1,0:05:21.02,0:05:22.44,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你都濒危了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.02,0:05:22.44,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You're endangered
Dialogue: 1,0:05:22.44,0:05:23.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那样不对的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.44,0:05:23.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Not like that
Dialogue: 1,0:05:23.47,0:05:27.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,胸怀爱心就能照顾好他
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.47,0:05:27.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,With lots of love and affection, we can take care of him
Dialogue: 1,0:05:29.46,0:05:31.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,小臭臭  到了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.46,0:05:31.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, smelly, here you are
Dialogue: 1,0:05:31.92,0:05:33.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你的新家
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.92,0:05:33.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Your new home
Dialogue: 1,0:05:33.02,0:05:35.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,小臭臭  一定会特别棒
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.02,0:05:35.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh, smelly, this is gonna be great
Dialogue: 1,0:05:35.42,0:05:38.08,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们马上就是快乐大家庭了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.42,0:05:38.08,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We'll be one big happy family
Dialogue: 1,0:05:38.08,0:05:39.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我带你参观一下
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.08,0:05:39.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Let me show you around
Dialogue: 1,0:05:39.20,0:05:40.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这是你的床  小臭臭
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.20,0:05:40.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Here's your bed, smelly
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.44,0:05:46.40,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(408,902)}小臭臭
Dialogue: 1,0:05:42.44,0:05:43.74,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这是你的食盆
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.44,0:05:43.74,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Here's your food bowl
Dialogue: 1,0:05:43.74,0:05:45.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,还有宠物粮
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.74,0:05:45.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And some kibble
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.78,0:05:44.86,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(596,534)}蜗牛粮
Dialogue: 1,0:05:46.40,0:05:49.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你可以住这儿一辈子了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.40,0:05:49.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You can live here forever and ever
Dialogue: 1,0:05:51.85,0:05:53.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,派大星你看
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.85,0:05:53.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Look, pat
Dialogue: 1,0:05:53.27,0:05:55.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他喜极而泣了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.27,0:05:55.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,He's crying tears of joy
Dialogue: 1,0:05:55.45,0:05:58.78,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,小臭臭  你还有一位家庭成员没见
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.45,0:05:57.46,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, smelly, there's one more
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.46,0:05:58.78,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,family member you haven't met
Dialogue: 1,0:05:59.42,0:06:01.01,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,小臭臭  这位是小蜗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.42,0:06:01.01,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Smelly, meet Gary
Dialogue: 1,0:06:01.89,0:06:03.49,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,快看啊  小臭臭
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.89,0:06:03.49,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Look at that, smelly
Dialogue: 1,0:06:03.49,0:06:05.29,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,小蜗喜欢你
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.49,0:06:05.29,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Gary likes you
Dialogue: 1,0:06:07.05,0:06:07.94,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,小蜗  不行
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.05,0:06:07.94,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Gary, no
Dialogue: 1,0:06:10.69,0:06:11.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,小蜗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.69,0:06:11.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Gary
Dialogue: 1,0:06:11.57,0:06:13.61,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,小蜗好像不喜欢小臭臭
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.57,0:06:13.61,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I don't think Gary likes smelly
Dialogue: 1,0:06:13.61,0:06:15.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,对啊  小蜗从来没那样攻击过别人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.61,0:06:15.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yeah, Gary's never attacked anyone like that
Dialogue: 1,0:06:15.92,0:06:16.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,除了章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.92,0:06:16.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,except Squidward
Dialogue: 1,0:06:16.77,0:06:18.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,看来小臭臭不能住这了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.77,0:06:18.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I guess smelly can't live here
Dialogue: 1,0:06:19.42,0:06:20.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他可以来跟我住
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.42,0:06:20.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,He can come live with me
Dialogue: 1,0:06:20.90,0:06:22.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,真是个好办法  派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.90,0:06:22.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's a great idea, Patrick
Dialogue: 1,0:06:22.57,0:06:24.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你一直都很想养宠物
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.57,0:06:24.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You've always wanted a pet
Dialogue: 1,0:06:27.42,0:06:28.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是不是很可爱
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.42,0:06:28.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Isn't that cute?
Dialogue: 1,0:06:28.75,0:06:30.66,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,看看他要住你家有多兴奋啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.75,0:06:30.66,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Look how excited he is to get to your house
Dialogue: 1,0:06:30.66,0:06:32.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,再见  小臭臭
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.66,0:06:32.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Bye, smelly
Dialogue: 1,0:06:32.05,0:06:33.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,祝你派大星家住得开心
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.05,0:06:33.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Have fun at Patrick's
Dialogue: 1,0:06:35.42,0:06:37.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不行  小臭臭
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.42,0:06:37.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No, no, smelly
Dialogue: 1,0:06:37.00,0:06:38.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,章鱼哥可不喜欢宠物
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.00,0:06:38.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Squidward doesn't like pets
Dialogue: 1,0:06:39.72,0:06:41.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,小臭臭  要玩捡球吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.72,0:06:41.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hey, smelly, wanna play catch?
Dialogue: 1,0:06:43.18,0:06:45.46,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,放心  你很快就学得会了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.18,0:06:45.46,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Don't worry, you'll get the hang of it
Dialogue: 1,0:06:46.67,0:06:47.69,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,差一点
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.67,0:06:47.69,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Almost
Dialogue: 1,0:06:47.69,0:06:48.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,再来
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.69,0:06:48.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Again
Dialogue: 1,0:06:49.92,0:06:50.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就差一点了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.92,0:06:50.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,So close
Dialogue: 1,0:06:51.62,0:06:52.88,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好  这下你
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.62,0:06:52.88,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yeah, now you're
Dialogue: 1,0:06:55.00,0:06:55.88,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,小臭臭
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.00,0:06:55.88,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Smelly
Dialogue: 1,0:06:56.35,0:06:57.61,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你什么毛病
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.35,0:06:57.61,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What's gotten into you?
Dialogue: 1,0:06:58.51,0:07:00.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,喂  动物管理局
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.51,0:07:00.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hello, animal control
Dialogue: 1,0:07:00.10,0:07:02.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我家闯进了只野生动物
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.10,0:07:02.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,There's a wild animal loose in my house
Dialogue: 1,0:07:02.82,0:07:03.71,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好  我不挂电话
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.82,0:07:03.71,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sure, I'll hold
Dialogue: 1,0:07:08.14,0:07:09.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,小臭臭  回来
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.14,0:07:09.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Smelly, come back
Dialogue: 1,0:07:09.95,0:07:12.49,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,小臭臭
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.95,0:07:12.49,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Smelly
Dialogue: 1,0:07:13.89,0:07:14.99,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不许动
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.89,0:07:14.99,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Freeze
Dialogue: 1,0:07:18.01,0:07:19.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这是在闹什么闹
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.01,0:07:19.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What's all the commotion
Dialogue: 1,0:07:20.96,0:07:22.04,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你们被包围了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.96,0:07:22.04,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You are surrounded
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.96,0:07:23.46,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(284,872)}动物园
Dialogue: 1,0:07:22.04,0:07:23.46,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,已经无路可逃了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.04,0:07:23.46,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,There is no way out
Dialogue: 1,0:07:23.46,0:07:24.46,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,小臭臭
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.46,0:07:24.46,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Smelly
Dialogue: 1,0:07:24.88,0:07:25.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.88,0:07:25.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Excuse me
Dialogue: 1,0:07:25.80,0:07:26.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,借过一下
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.80,0:07:26.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Pardon me
Dialogue: 1,0:07:26.50,0:07:28.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,挪过去就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.50,0:07:28.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,If I can just scooch through there
Dialogue: 1,0:07:28.37,0:07:29.11,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.37,0:07:29.11,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Excuse me
Dialogue: 1,0:07:29.11,0:07:29.63,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,借过一下
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.11,0:07:29.63,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Pardon me
Dialogue: 1,0:07:29.63,0:07:30.34,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.63,0:07:30.34,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Excuse me
Dialogue: 1,0:07:30.72,0:07:32.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你们别来烦小臭臭
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.72,0:07:32.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You leave smelly alone
Dialogue: 1,0:07:32.47,0:07:35.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他就只是只可怜又呆傻的野生动物
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.47,0:07:35.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,He's just a poor, dumb, wild animal
Dialogue: 1,0:07:35.60,0:07:37.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,野生动物不属于这里  小子
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.60,0:07:37.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Wild animals don't belong here, son
Dialogue: 1,0:07:37.60,0:07:38.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,只属于动物园
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.60,0:07:38.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,They belong in the zoo
Dialogue: 1,0:07:38.75,0:07:39.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,抓起来
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.75,0:07:39.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Get him, boys
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.81,0:07:46.73,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(630,732)}动物园
Dialogue: 1,0:07:53.12,0:07:54.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,小臭臭
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.12,0:07:54.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Smelly
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.45,0:07:57.08,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1140,308)}不明物种
Dialogue: 1,0:07:57.08,0:07:59.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,妈妈  那是什么怪东西
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.08,0:07:59.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Mommy, what is that thing?
Dialogue: 1,0:07:59.42,0:08:01.83,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不知道  不过它丑死了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.42,0:08:01.83,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I don't know, but it's hideous, isn't it?
Dialogue: 1,0:08:06.42,0:08:07.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这可不好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.42,0:08:07.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This isn't good
Dialogue: 1,0:08:07.37,0:08:08.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你说得可对了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.37,0:08:08.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You're absolutely right
Dialogue: 1,0:08:09.47,0:08:10.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,它得加芥末酱
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.47,0:08:10.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It needs mustard
Dialogue: 1,0:08:10.80,0:08:12.54,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,谁都不应该被那样对待
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.80,0:08:12.54,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No one should be treated like that
Dialogue: 1,0:08:12.54,0:08:14.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,更何况是跟小臭臭一样丑的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.54,0:08:14.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Not even someone as ugly as smelly
Dialogue: 1,0:08:14.97,0:08:16.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这种事一定要让我们出手
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.97,0:08:16.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Something needs to be done about this
Dialogue: 1,0:08:16.80,0:08:19.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,而我正好知道怎么出手
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.80,0:08:19.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and I know exactly what that thing is
Dialogue: 1,0:08:23.98,0:08:24.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好的  派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.98,0:08:24.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,OK, Patrick
Dialogue: 1,0:08:24.97,0:08:25.98,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,还记得计划吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.97,0:08:25.98,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Remember the plan?
Dialogue: 1,0:08:26.50,0:08:27.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,记得
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.50,0:08:27.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yeah
Dialogue: 1,0:08:27.23,0:08:28.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是这个吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.23,0:08:28.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This one, right?
Dialogue: 1,0:08:28.15,0:08:29.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不是那个
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.15,0:08:29.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No, not that
Dialogue: 1,0:08:29.65,0:08:33.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我说的是让小臭臭越狱的计划
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.65,0:08:30.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm talking about the plan
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.82,0:08:33.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,to break smelly out of this animal prison
Dialogue: 1,0:08:33.86,0:08:34.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好计划
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.86,0:08:34.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Good plan
Dialogue: 1,0:08:36.16,0:08:38.01,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好  我先下
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.16,0:08:38.01,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,All right, I'll go down first
Dialogue: 1,0:08:38.01,0:08:39.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,注意警戒  跟紧我
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.01,0:08:39.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Keep a lookout and follow me
Dialogue: 1,0:08:42.27,0:08:43.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你是我的英雄
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.27,0:08:43.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You're my hero
Dialogue: 1,0:08:45.74,0:08:46.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.74,0:08:46.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hey, SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:08:47.13,0:08:47.88,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,救命
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.13,0:08:47.88,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Help
Dialogue: 1,0:08:50.45,0:08:51.46,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,会被抓的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.45,0:08:51.46,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We'll get caught
Dialogue: 1,0:08:52.78,0:08:54.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,什么  我听不见
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.78,0:08:54.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What, I can't hear you
Dialogue: 1,0:08:54.00,0:08:55.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我喊得太大声了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.00,0:08:55.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm screaming too loud
Dialogue: 1,0:09:04.42,0:09:06.79,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不用再怕了  亲爱的小臭臭
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.42,0:09:06.79,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Fear no longer, dear smelly
Dialogue: 1,0:09:06.79,0:09:08.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们来救你了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.79,0:09:08.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We are here to rescue you
Dialogue: 1,0:09:08.65,0:09:10.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,明白吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.65,0:09:10.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Understand?
Dialogue: 1,0:09:10.53,0:09:15.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们来接你回家
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.53,0:09:15.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We are taking you home
Dialogue: 1,0:09:16.36,0:09:17.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,看他有多兴奋啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.36,0:09:17.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Look how excited he is
Dialogue: 1,0:09:17.87,0:09:19.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,开关打开  派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.87,0:09:19.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Flip the switch, Patrick
Dialogue: 1,0:09:24.41,0:09:26.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,小臭臭  你自由了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.41,0:09:26.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Smelly, you're free
Dialogue: 1,0:09:32.29,0:09:33.51,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你们被包围了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.29,0:09:33.51,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You're surrounded
Dialogue: 1,0:09:33.51,0:09:34.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,逃也没用
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.51,0:09:34.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,There's no use trying to run
Dialogue: 1,0:09:34.97,0:09:36.51,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,派大星  快逃啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.97,0:09:36.51,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Run, Patrick, run
Dialogue: 1,0:09:46.57,0:09:47.84,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,快一点  派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.57,0:09:47.84,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Faster, Patrick
Dialogue: 1,0:09:57.01,0:09:58.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我会让小臭臭先跑
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.01,0:09:58.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'll let smelly go first
Dialogue: 1,0:10:04.48,0:10:05.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,别怕  小臭臭
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.48,0:10:05.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Don't worry, smelly
Dialogue: 1,0:10:05.60,0:10:06.79,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你有我们肯定安全
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.60,0:10:06.79,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You're safe with us
Dialogue: 1,0:10:10.21,0:10:11.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,应该甩掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.21,0:10:11.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Think we lost 'em
Dialogue: 1,0:10:12.45,0:10:15.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们又是快乐大家庭了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.45,0:10:15.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, we're all one big happy family again
Dialogue: 1,0:10:15.75,0:10:17.96,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,来看看这黑漆漆的下水道通向哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.75,0:10:17.96,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Let's see where this dark sewer tunnel leads
Dialogue: 1,0:10:22.09,0:10:23.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没事的  小臭臭
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.09,0:10:23.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's all right, smelly
Dialogue: 1,0:10:23.70,0:10:24.61,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们马上就能回到家
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.70,0:10:24.61,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Soon we'll be home
Dialogue: 1,0:10:24.61,0:10:25.54,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你马上就能睡在
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.61,0:10:25.54,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and you can sleep in that
Dialogue: 1,0:10:25.54,0:10:27.99,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你心爱又舒服的宠物提篮里了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.54,0:10:27.99,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,cozy little pet carrier you love so much
Dialogue: 1,0:10:31.19,0:10:32.06,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我看到光了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.19,0:10:32.06,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I see light
Dialogue: 1,0:10:32.06,0:10:33.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,还真是  派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.06,0:10:33.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You're right, Patrick
Dialogue: 1,0:10:33.17,0:10:34.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那一定就是出口
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.17,0:10:34.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,that must be the way out
Dialogue: 1,0:10:35.85,0:10:37.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那是什么地方
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.85,0:10:37.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Where are we?
Dialogue: 1,0:10:40.00,0:10:41.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,去问他们吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.00,0:10:41.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Let's go ask those guys
Dialogue: 1,0:10:42.15,0:10:43.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.15,0:10:43.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Excuse us?
Dialogue: 1,0:10:45.52,0:10:47.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他们跟你长得好像
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.52,0:10:47.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,They look just like you
Dialogue: 1,0:10:47.54,0:10:49.96,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,去吧  陪你真正的家人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.54,0:10:49.96,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Go, be with your real family
Dialogue: 1,0:10:49.96,0:10:51.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,快去吧  小臭臭
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.96,0:10:51.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Go ahead, smelly
Dialogue: 1,0:10:54.75,0:10:57.14,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我知道你把我们当家人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.75,0:10:57.14,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I know you've come to think of us as a family
Dialogue: 1,0:10:57.14,0:10:59.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,但是这样才更好
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.14,0:10:59.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,but it's better this way
Dialogue: 1,0:11:08.81,0:11:10.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我会想念他的  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.81,0:11:10.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna miss him, SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:11:10.80,0:11:11.81,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我也是  兄弟
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.80,0:11:11.81,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Me too, buddy
Dialogue: 1,0:11:12.00,0:11:12.64,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我也是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.00,0:11:12.64,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Me too
Dialogue: 1,0:11:12.64,0:11:15.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,但他现在陪着同类  他属于那个地方
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.64,0:11:15.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But he's with his own kind now, where he belongs
Dialogue: 1,0:11:15.60,0:11:19.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,既然如此  回到属于我们的地方吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.60,0:11:19.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And on that note, let us go back to where we belong
Dialogue: 1,0:11:30.22,0:11:32.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你们好  我的孩子们
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.22,0:11:32.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Salutations, my children
Dialogue: 1,0:11:32.30,0:11:36.24,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,准备好聆听每日一曲轻柔爵士了没
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.30,0:11:36.24,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Are you ready for your daily dose of smooth jazz?
Dialogue: 1,0:11:50.84,0:11:51.49,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,嗨
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.84,0:11:51.49,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hi
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.27,0:11:55.86,起司 一般标题,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\c&H00FFC1&}天灵灵\N{\fs40} \N{\fs175}地灵灵
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.02,0:11:58.19,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\frz29.74\pos(245.316,450)}分镜总监
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.02,0:11:58.19,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\frz29.74\pos(495.678,728)}编剧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.02,0:12:00.69,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1096,976.667)}翻译{\fnArial}: 1440kHz
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.40,0:12:00.69,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\frz29.52\pos(401.566,448)}技术总监
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.40,0:12:00.69,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\frz29.52\pos(527.736,700)}动画总监
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.86,0:12:03.32,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\frz29.29\pos(421.602,536)}制片指导
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.86,0:12:03.32,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1034.667,976.667)}本字幕仅限学习交流\N严禁用于商业用途
Dialogue: 1,0:12:06.15,0:12:07.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,加油  炉子
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.15,0:12:07.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Come on, "stovey"
Dialogue: 1,0:12:07.75,0:12:09.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,快爆啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.75,0:12:09.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,pop that corn
Dialogue: 1,0:12:11.02,0:12:12.54,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,准备好  小蜗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.02,0:12:12.54,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Get ready, Gary
Dialogue: 1,0:12:15.27,0:12:16.63,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,要来了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.27,0:12:16.63,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Incoming
Dialogue: 1,0:12:25.26,0:12:27.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,爆米花好了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.26,0:12:27.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Popcorn is served
Dialogue: 1,0:12:31.58,0:12:34.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那位老兄是洗车场的克星
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.58,0:12:34.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That bro is trouble at any car wash
Dialogue: 1,0:12:34.52,0:12:38.36,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,广告过后继续收看  裤头村洗车场
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.52,0:12:36.81,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We will return to Bikini Bottom car wash
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.81,0:12:38.36,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,after these messages
Dialogue: 1,0:12:38.77,0:12:40.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你是个无聊的人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.77,0:12:40.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Are you boring?
Dialogue: 1,0:12:40.92,0:12:43.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,对  我无聊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.92,0:12:43.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yes, yes I am
Dialogue: 1,0:12:43.10,0:12:49.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你朋友会用枯燥乏味这四字形容你吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.10,0:12:45.03,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,When friends describe you
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.03,0:12:49.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,do they use words like "dull," or "drab?"
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.49,0:12:47.32,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(260,472)}枯燥
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.62,0:12:48.70,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1076,496)}乏味
Dialogue: 1,0:12:50.63,0:12:52.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,还有平凡这俩字
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.63,0:12:52.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Don't forget "platitudinous"
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.00,0:12:55.12,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1034,584)}平凡
Dialogue: 1,0:12:55.72,0:12:57.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,还真是  查理
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.72,0:12:57.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yes, that too, Charlie
Dialogue: 1,0:12:57.87,0:13:01.53,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,但要是我对你说  你能改变那一切呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.87,0:13:01.53,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But what if I told you that you could change all that
Dialogue: 1,0:13:01.53,0:13:03.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,只要有神奇的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.53,0:13:03.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,with the magic of
Dialogue: 1,0:13:03.32,0:13:05.29,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,魔法
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.32,0:13:05.29,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,magic
Dialogue: 1,0:13:09.88,0:13:12.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我样子好像个魔法师
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.88,0:13:12.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I look like some kind of magician
Dialogue: 1,0:13:12.30,0:13:14.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这下我不会被无视了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.30,0:13:14.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now people won't ignore me
Dialogue: 1,0:13:14.80,0:13:17.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,但愿是这样  查理
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.80,0:13:17.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Let's hope not, Charlie
Dialogue: 1,0:13:17.00,0:13:20.16,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,大法师神奇魔法装备在手
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.00,0:13:20.16,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,With my Mr. Magic magical magic kit
Dialogue: 1,0:13:20.16,0:13:23.91,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就连你都能惊艳你朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.16,0:13:23.91,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,even you can impress and amaze your friends
Dialogue: 1,0:13:23.91,0:13:26.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我想惊艳我朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.91,0:13:26.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I want to impress and amaze my friends
Dialogue: 1,0:13:26.07,0:13:30.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,把十九块九毛五汇给我大法师
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.07,0:13:30.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Just send $1995 to me, Mr. Magic
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.33,0:13:40.00,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(686,552)}裤头村邮局
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.00,0:13:44.51,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(368,196)}寄件
Dialogue: 1,0:13:44.51,0:13:46.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,75,,四到六周后
Dialogue: 1,0:13:48.79,0:13:52.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,一套魔法装备  还有个黄色玩意
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.79,0:13:52.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,One magic kit, and another one of these yellow things
Dialogue: 1,0:14:01.23,0:14:02.19,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,到货了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.23,0:14:02.19,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Here it is
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.19,0:14:04.61,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1022,192)}大法师神奇魔法装备
Dialogue: 1,0:14:02.19,0:14:04.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,大法师神奇魔法装备
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.19,0:14:04.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Mr. Magic's magical magic kit
Dialogue: 1,0:14:07.53,0:14:08.99,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,看看这么多好货
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.53,0:14:08.99,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Look at all this
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.99,0:14:09.95,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1186,372)}咒语书
Dialogue: 1,0:14:08.99,0:14:12.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,一本咒语书  我专属的奇想魔杖
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.99,0:14:12.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,A book of spells, my very own wand of whimsy
Dialogue: 1,0:14:13.22,0:14:14.89,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,妖僧拉斯普京之须
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.22,0:14:14.89,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The beard of Rasputin
Dialogue: 1,0:14:15.47,0:14:18.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,当然还有  至关重要的修炼法术执照
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.47,0:14:17.54,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And of course, the all-important license
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.54,0:14:18.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,to practice magic
Dialogue: 1,0:14:23.21,0:14:24.36,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.21,0:14:24.36,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Squidward
Dialogue: 1,0:14:24.36,0:14:26.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他一定会欣赏我新学到的法力
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.36,0:14:26.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,He'll appreciate my newly-delivered skill
Dialogue: 1,0:14:26.60,0:14:30.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,盐汽水  低脂海草片
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.60,0:14:30.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Brine soda, low-fat seaweed crisps
Dialogue: 1,0:14:30.35,0:14:31.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,冷爵士
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.35,0:14:31.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,cool jazz
Dialogue: 1,0:14:34.52,0:14:35.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,章鱼哥  又办到了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.52,0:14:35.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Squidward, you have done it
Dialogue: 1,0:14:36.08,0:14:39.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你都把自己给惯坏了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.08,0:14:39.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You have officially spoiled yourself rotten
Dialogue: 1,0:14:39.55,0:14:42.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那你就继续惯坏自己吧  朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.55,0:14:42.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, let the rotting continue, friend
Dialogue: 1,0:14:42.10,0:14:45.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我要惊艳你  使出
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.10,0:14:45.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,while I impress and amaze you with
Dialogue: 1,0:14:45.35,0:14:47.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,魔法
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.35,0:14:47.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,magic
Dialogue: 1,0:14:48.12,0:14:48.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,魔法吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.12,0:14:48.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Magic?
Dialogue: 1,0:14:48.95,0:14:51.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你能让自己消失吗  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.95,0:14:51.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Can you make yourself disappear, SpongeBob?
Dialogue: 1,0:14:53.15,0:14:54.41,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,章鱼哥笨死了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.15,0:14:54.41,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Silly Squidward
Dialogue: 1,0:14:54.70,0:14:57.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,得升上十级法师才能学消失咒
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.70,0:14:55.99,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I won't learn vanishing spells
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.99,0:14:57.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,until I become a level 10 wizard
Dialogue: 1,0:14:58.41,0:15:00.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,最好先从简单点的法术施起
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.41,0:15:00.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No, I'd better start with something simpler
Dialogue: 1,0:15:00.17,0:15:01.83,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,来召唤卡牌
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.17,0:15:01.83,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Say, card conjuring
Dialogue: 1,0:15:02.19,0:15:04.34,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,给  拿着这张单纯的卡牌
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.19,0:15:04.34,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Here, hold this simple playing card
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.34,0:15:08.26,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(544,792)}咒语书
Dialogue: 1,0:15:04.34,0:15:10.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我要在你眼前把它变成魔法卡牌
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.34,0:15:08.26,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,while I transform it into a magic playing card
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.26,0:15:10.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,before your very eyes
Dialogue: 1,0:15:10.15,0:15:10.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,来看看
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.15,0:15:10.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Let's see
Dialogue: 1,0:15:11.60,0:15:13.19,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,第一步
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.60,0:15:13.19,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Step one
Dialogue: 1,0:15:14.70,0:15:17.64,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,一时半会儿多半做不完
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.70,0:15:17.64,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This can't possibly end soon
Dialogue: 1,0:15:17.64,0:15:19.89,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,紧接着就是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.64,0:15:19.89,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Which brings us to
Dialogue: 1,0:15:20.21,0:15:21.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,第三步
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.21,0:15:21.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Step three
Dialogue: 1,0:15:21.57,0:15:22.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,杂耍东西
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.57,0:15:22.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Juggle something
Dialogue: 1,0:15:22.47,0:15:24.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,耍就耍吧  大法师
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.47,0:15:24.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, if you insist, Mr. Magic
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.78,0:15:31.78,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1054,294)}公交站
Dialogue: 1,0:15:33.88,0:15:36.49,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不管你去哪  总之带我走就对了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.88,0:15:34.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I don't care where you're going
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.87,0:15:36.49,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,just take me away from here
Dialogue: 1,0:15:36.67,0:15:39.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,然后  拿出一张牌塞你耳朵里
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.67,0:15:39.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Then, take one card and shove it in your ear
Dialogue: 1,0:15:43.62,0:15:46.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可我不喜欢开心果
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.62,0:15:46.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But I don't like pistachio
Dialogue: 1,0:15:46.25,0:15:48.13,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那你干嘛要开心果味的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.25,0:15:48.13,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Then why did you ask for it?
Dialogue: 1,0:15:52.05,0:15:56.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,最后念咒语  天灵灵海灵灵
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.05,0:15:56.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And finally, just say the words "hobris-pobris"
Dialogue: 1,0:15:59.25,0:16:00.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.25,0:16:00.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Squidward
Dialogue: 1,0:16:00.57,0:16:03.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我简单的卡牌魔法把你变成冰淇淋了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.57,0:16:01.64,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,My simple card trick
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.64,0:16:03.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,has turned you into an ice cream cone
Dialogue: 1,0:16:03.77,0:16:04.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,所以说
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.77,0:16:04.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Which means
Dialogue: 1,0:16:05.40,0:16:07.53,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我就是十级法师
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.40,0:16:07.53,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I am a level 10 wizard
Dialogue: 1,0:16:07.53,0:16:10.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,看来该把你变回章鱼形态了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.53,0:16:10.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I suppose I should change you back to squid form
Dialogue: 1,0:16:11.40,0:16:12.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我变
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.40,0:16:12.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Presto
Dialogue: 1,0:16:13.86,0:16:15.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,来看看
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.86,0:16:15.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Let's see
Dialogue: 1,0:16:16.30,0:16:17.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,阿拉卡扎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.30,0:16:17.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,A-la-kazam
Dialogue: 1,0:16:21.21,0:16:22.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,阿布拉卡达布拉
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.21,0:16:22.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Abracadabra
Dialogue: 1,0:16:24.42,0:16:25.21,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,乌格里度格里
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.42,0:16:25.21,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oogly-doogly
Dialogue: 1,0:16:26.46,0:16:27.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,活不拉括不拉
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.46,0:16:27.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hobra-cobra
Dialogue: 1,0:16:28.17,0:16:29.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,芝麻开门
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.17,0:16:29.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Open sesame?
Dialogue: 1,0:16:30.19,0:16:32.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,求你变回章鱼哥咒
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.19,0:16:32.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Change-oh back-oh to Squidward-oh, please-oh
Dialogue: 1,0:16:34.47,0:16:36.78,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,真对不起  章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.47,0:16:36.78,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I am so sorry, Squidward
Dialogue: 1,0:16:37.35,0:16:40.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我害你变成了美味的乳味冰淇淋
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.35,0:16:40.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I've transformed you into a delicious dairy dessert
Dialogue: 1,0:16:40.50,0:16:43.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,结果变不回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.50,0:16:43.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and I can't change you back
Dialogue: 1,0:16:44.73,0:16:46.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没事的  章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.73,0:16:46.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,There, there, Squidward
Dialogue: 1,0:16:46.55,0:16:48.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没必要哭的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.55,0:16:48.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,There is no need to cry
Dialogue: 1,0:16:48.32,0:16:50.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我发誓  你一定会恢复原状
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.32,0:16:50.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I promise you will continue your normal life
Dialogue: 1,0:16:50.87,0:16:53.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,虽然你现在可以吃
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.87,0:16:53.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,despite the fact that you are now edible
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.28,0:16:54.95,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(992,400)}礁石影院
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.80,0:17:15.72,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(686,262)}冰
Dialogue: 1,0:17:19.03,0:17:21.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,章鱼哥  跟我说话啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.03,0:17:21.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Squidward, speak to me
Dialogue: 1,0:17:21.56,0:17:23.16,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,说话啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.56,0:17:23.16,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Speak
Dialogue: 1,0:17:34.11,0:17:34.74,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.11,0:17:34.74,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hey, squid
Dialogue: 1,0:17:34.86,0:17:35.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.86,0:17:35.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Are you OK?
Dialogue: 1,0:17:37.16,0:17:37.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.16,0:17:37.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hey, squid
Dialogue: 1,0:17:37.82,0:17:38.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你现在还没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.82,0:17:38.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Are you still OK?
Dialogue: 1,0:17:43.76,0:17:44.81,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.76,0:17:44.81,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hey, Squidward
Dialogue: 1,0:17:44.81,0:17:46.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我有东西要给你
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.81,0:17:46.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I got something for you
Dialogue: 1,0:17:46.71,0:17:49.53,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是个伴  陪你一起坐在乏味的冰箱里
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.71,0:17:49.53,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Someone to keep you company in that drab old freezer
Dialogue: 1,0:17:51.01,0:17:52.71,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他们真可爱啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.01,0:17:52.71,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Aren't they cute?
Dialogue: 1,0:17:53.69,0:17:56.74,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我发誓要永远守护我的好朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.69,0:17:56.74,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I promise to stand by as an eternal guard over my buddy
Dialogue: 1,0:17:58.02,0:17:59.16,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.02,0:17:59.16,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hey, SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:17:59.16,0:18:00.01,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你在干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.16,0:18:00.01,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What you doing?
Dialogue: 1,0:18:00.01,0:18:02.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我把可怜的章鱼哥变成了冰淇淋
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.01,0:18:02.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I have turned poor Squidward into a frozen dessert
Dialogue: 1,0:18:02.70,0:18:03.81,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,太糟了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.70,0:18:03.81,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's awful
Dialogue: 1,0:18:04.47,0:18:05.81,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,真惨啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.47,0:18:05.81,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,How tragic
Dialogue: 1,0:18:06.64,0:18:07.53,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,章鱼哥真可怜
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.64,0:18:07.53,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Poor Squidward
Dialogue: 1,0:18:07.72,0:18:09.56,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,都是我的错
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.72,0:18:09.56,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's all my fault
Dialogue: 1,0:18:09.56,0:18:11.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你刚说了冰淇淋吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.56,0:18:11.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Did you say frozen dessert?
Dialogue: 1,0:18:11.07,0:18:15.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,对  我把他变成了华夫蛋筒软冰淇淋
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.07,0:18:13.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I turned him into a tasty soft serve
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.90,0:18:15.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,with a waffle cone
Dialogue: 1,0:18:17.24,0:18:18.68,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,软冰淇淋啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.24,0:18:18.68,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Soft serve
Dialogue: 1,0:18:18.92,0:18:19.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.92,0:18:19.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Patrick
Dialogue: 1,0:18:19.92,0:18:21.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,别吃章鱼哥了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.92,0:18:21.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Stop eating Squidward
Dialogue: 1,0:18:23.00,0:18:23.68,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.00,0:18:23.68,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sorry
Dialogue: 1,0:18:25.13,0:18:25.83,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.13,0:18:25.83,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Patrick
Dialogue: 1,0:18:28.37,0:18:29.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可他真太好吃了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.37,0:18:29.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But he's so tasty
Dialogue: 1,0:18:32.39,0:18:34.88,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,派大星  你就没听懂吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.39,0:18:34.88,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Look, Patrick, don't you understand?
Dialogue: 1,0:18:34.88,0:18:37.34,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这根本就不是你平时吃的冰淇淋
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.88,0:18:37.34,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This isn't just your ordinary ice cream cone
Dialogue: 1,0:18:37.34,0:18:38.63,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是开心果味的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.34,0:18:38.63,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's pistachio
Dialogue: 1,0:18:38.63,0:18:41.39,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不对  那是章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.63,0:18:41.39,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No, it's Squidward
Dialogue: 1,0:18:41.39,0:18:42.59,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不管出了什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.39,0:18:42.59,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And no matter what happens
Dialogue: 1,0:18:42.59,0:18:44.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我都答应过要看护他
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.59,0:18:44.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I promised him that I would watch over him
Dialogue: 1,0:18:44.47,0:18:47.64,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就算他变软冰淇淋  也要让他好好活
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.47,0:18:47.64,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,to ensure his soft frozen life is unchanged
Dialogue: 1,0:18:52.32,0:18:53.04,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.32,0:18:53.04,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Patrick
Dialogue: 1,0:18:53.04,0:18:54.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,章鱼哥融化了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.04,0:18:54.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Squidward has melted
Dialogue: 1,0:18:54.50,0:18:56.09,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,快报警啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.50,0:18:56.09,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Quick, call the police
Dialogue: 1,0:18:56.39,0:18:57.48,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我该怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.39,0:18:57.48,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What am I gonna do?
Dialogue: 1,0:18:57.98,0:19:00.74,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海神王啊  全都要怪我
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.98,0:19:00.74,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh, Neptune, it's all my fault
Dialogue: 1,0:19:00.74,0:19:03.06,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我干了什么
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.74,0:19:03.06,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What have I done?
Dialogue: 1,0:19:03.31,0:19:04.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我干了什么
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.31,0:19:04.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What have I done?
Dialogue: 1,0:19:04.47,0:19:05.13,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我干了什么
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.47,0:19:05.13,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What have I done?
Dialogue: 1,0:19:05.58,0:19:06.34,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我干了什么
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.58,0:19:06.34,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What have I done?
Dialogue: 1,0:19:07.40,0:19:08.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,全都要怪你
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.40,0:19:08.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's all your fault
Dialogue: 1,0:19:10.32,0:19:13.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我诅咒你  大法师神奇魔法装备
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.32,0:19:13.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Curse you, Mr. Magic magical magic kit
Dialogue: 1,0:19:13.55,0:19:14.69,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我诅咒你
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.55,0:19:14.69,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Curse you
Dialogue: 1,0:19:15.50,0:19:16.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,有了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.50,0:19:16.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's it
Dialogue: 1,0:19:16.45,0:19:18.41,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,问题的答案出现了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.45,0:19:18.41,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,There's the answer to our problems
Dialogue: 1,0:19:18.67,0:19:19.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,警告
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.67,0:19:19.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,"Warning
Dialogue: 1,0:19:19.50,0:19:21.64,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,仅限9至99岁玩耍
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.50,0:19:21.64,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,From ages nine to 99"
Dialogue: 1,0:19:21.94,0:19:22.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不对  派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.94,0:19:22.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No, Patrick
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.72,0:19:26.68,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(402,830)}大法师企业\N海洋裤头村\N魔法师{\fnArial}1942{\c&HFFFFFF&\fnAdobe 黑体 Std R}号
Dialogue: 1,0:19:22.72,0:19:24.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是那个能帮上忙的大神
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.72,0:19:24.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The one mystic being that can help us
Dialogue: 1,0:19:24.97,0:19:26.13,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,大法师
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.97,0:19:26.13,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Mr. Magic
Dialogue: 1,0:19:26.89,0:19:28.86,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,顺着棕色的砖瓦路走
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.89,0:19:28.86,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Just follow the brown tile road
Dialogue: 1,0:19:28.86,0:19:31.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,去寻找最神秘的大师
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.86,0:19:31.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,to the most mysterious mystic of 'em all
Dialogue: 1,0:19:31.10,0:19:32.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,从来没有谁亲眼见过他
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.10,0:19:32.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No one's ever seen him in person
Dialogue: 1,0:19:33.17,0:19:34.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,请进
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.17,0:19:34.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Enter
Dialogue: 1,0:19:41.72,0:19:45.24,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,谁这么大胆  敢来见大法师
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.72,0:19:45.24,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Who dares to see Mr. Magic?
Dialogue: 1,0:19:46.58,0:19:47.66,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,报上名来
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.58,0:19:47.66,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Speak up
Dialogue: 1,0:19:47.87,0:19:51.13,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是我  海绵那个宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.87,0:19:51.13,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It is I, SpongeBob of the SquarePants
Dialogue: 1,0:19:51.13,0:19:52.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,一级魔法师
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.13,0:19:52.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,magician level one
Dialogue: 1,0:19:52.70,0:19:55.38,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我把我朋友变成冰淇淋了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.70,0:19:55.38,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And I have changed my friend into ice cream
Dialogue: 1,0:19:56.38,0:19:57.63,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,表现得不错
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.38,0:19:57.63,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Good job
Dialogue: 1,0:19:57.63,0:19:58.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,多谢了  可是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.63,0:19:58.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, thank you, but
Dialogue: 1,0:19:59.21,0:20:00.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我没法把他给变回去啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.21,0:20:00.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, I can't change him back
Dialogue: 1,0:20:02.47,0:20:04.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,有没有考虑过换个爱好
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.47,0:20:04.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, have you ever thought of a different hobby?
Dialogue: 1,0:20:04.72,0:20:07.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我需要你帮忙把他变回来
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.72,0:20:07.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I need your help to change him back
Dialogue: 1,0:20:07.20,0:20:08.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我帮忙吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.20,0:20:08.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,My help?
Dialogue: 1,0:20:08.75,0:20:09.56,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,还是免了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.75,0:20:09.56,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No thank you
Dialogue: 1,0:20:09.56,0:20:12.39,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你不帮忙  我朋友永远都变不回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.56,0:20:12.39,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But if you don't, my friend will be a cone forever
Dialogue: 1,0:20:12.39,0:20:14.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,抱歉  我
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.39,0:20:14.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sorry, I, um
Dialogue: 1,0:20:14.50,0:20:15.64,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我  去吃午饭了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.50,0:20:15.64,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm, out to lunch
Dialogue: 1,0:20:15.64,0:20:16.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就这样
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.64,0:20:16.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,that's it
Dialogue: 1,0:20:16.20,0:20:16.81,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我可以等
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.20,0:20:16.81,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'll wait
Dialogue: 1,0:20:17.07,0:20:18.61,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我这午饭得吃两年
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.07,0:20:18.61,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm on a two-year lunch
Dialogue: 1,0:20:18.61,0:20:19.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,拜托
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.61,0:20:19.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh, please
Dialogue: 1,0:20:19.90,0:20:21.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,别吵
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.90,0:20:21.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Silence
Dialogue: 1,0:20:21.20,0:20:24.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可是法师  别人都没有你这般的法力
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.20,0:20:24.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But sir, no one else has your power of sorcery
Dialogue: 1,0:20:24.92,0:20:26.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.92,0:20:26.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Thank you
Dialogue: 1,0:20:26.62,0:20:30.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝  那边有个谁对着管子讲话
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.62,0:20:28.74,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hey, SpongeBob, there's a guy over here
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.74,0:20:30.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,talking into a tubey thing
Dialogue: 1,0:20:31.22,0:20:32.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,别理你朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.22,0:20:32.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Ignore your friend
Dialogue: 1,0:20:32.65,0:20:35.96,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你看到的鱼只是个幻象
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.65,0:20:35.96,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The fish you see is only an illusion
Dialogue: 1,0:20:36.47,0:20:39.66,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他怎么在跟大法师说一样的话
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.47,0:20:39.66,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Why's he saying the same thing Mr. Magic's saying?
Dialogue: 1,0:20:39.98,0:20:41.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不知道  派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.98,0:20:41.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I don't know, Patrick
Dialogue: 1,0:20:41.70,0:20:43.38,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你是谁  先生
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.70,0:20:43.38,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Who are you, good sir?
Dialogue: 1,0:20:43.38,0:20:44.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那个
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.38,0:20:44.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, uh
Dialogue: 1,0:20:44.86,0:20:47.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我是霍瑞斯达法师
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.86,0:20:47.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm Horace B. Magic
Dialogue: 1,0:20:47.55,0:20:50.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你就是大法师吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.55,0:20:50.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Are you Mr. Magic?
Dialogue: 1,0:20:50.96,0:20:52.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,真名确实就那个
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.96,0:20:52.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Technically, yes
Dialogue: 1,0:20:52.87,0:20:56.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,但这里真正的魔法就是生意的魔法
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.87,0:20:56.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But the only magic around here is the magic of business
Dialogue: 1,0:20:56.57,0:20:59.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,所以说你没法把我朋友变回来了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.57,0:20:59.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Does that mean you can't change my friend back?
Dialogue: 1,0:21:00.63,0:21:02.19,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,恐怕没法了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.63,0:21:02.19,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm afraid not
Dialogue: 1,0:21:02.19,0:21:04.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,真遗憾  小子
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.19,0:21:04.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,So sorry about that, laddie
Dialogue: 1,0:21:04.27,0:21:05.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,退款支票已经邮寄给你了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.27,0:21:05.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Your refund check is in the mail
Dialogue: 1,0:21:05.80,0:21:07.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我不需要退款
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.80,0:21:07.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I don't need a refund
Dialogue: 1,0:21:07.07,0:21:08.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我只想救回我朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.07,0:21:08.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I want my friend back
Dialogue: 1,0:21:08.60,0:21:10.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,根本就不是钱的问题
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.60,0:21:10.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This isn't about money
Dialogue: 1,0:21:10.55,0:21:12.08,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你就只是个假货
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.55,0:21:12.08,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You're nothing but a fake
Dialogue: 1,0:21:12.08,0:21:14.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,骗人的集团商人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.08,0:21:14.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Just a lying, corporate businessman
Dialogue: 1,0:21:14.52,0:21:18.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你纸醉金迷  玷污了魔法
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.52,0:21:16.04,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,tainting the purity of magic
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.04,0:21:18.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,with your corrupt, commercial ways
Dialogue: 1,0:21:18.60,0:21:21.74,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你害我对魔法失去了信任
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.60,0:21:21.74,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You have ruined my faith in the magical arts
Dialogue: 1,0:21:26.35,0:21:27.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,保安
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.35,0:21:27.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Security
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.26,0:21:28.85,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(986,106)}出口
Dialogue: 1,0:21:32.22,0:21:34.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,章鱼哥要怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.22,0:21:34.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What are we gonna do about Squidward?
Dialogue: 1,0:21:34.02,0:21:35.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,随时都能吃了他
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.02,0:21:35.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We could always eat him
Dialogue: 1,0:21:35.94,0:21:36.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我都有点饿了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.94,0:21:36.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm kind of hungry
Dialogue: 1,0:21:37.98,0:21:39.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,大法师是假的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.98,0:21:39.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Mr. Magic was a fake
Dialogue: 1,0:21:39.67,0:21:41.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他的魔法玩意也都是假的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.67,0:21:41.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And all of his magic stuff is fake
Dialogue: 1,0:21:41.70,0:21:43.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那些咒语也都是假的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.70,0:21:43.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,All those magic words, they were fake
Dialogue: 1,0:21:43.85,0:21:46.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,压基沙基扒皮大皮
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.85,0:21:46.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yacky, schmacky, bappy, dappy
Dialogue: 1,0:21:46.12,0:21:48.03,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,多皮剥皮把比法比
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.12,0:21:48.03,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,doppy, boppy, blabby, flabby
Dialogue: 1,0:21:51.29,0:21:55.53,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,扎皮嘎咒比皮比皮八米加
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.29,0:21:55.53,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,zappiga zowie, blippy bippy, blammica
Dialogue: 1,0:21:56.83,0:21:58.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你在干什么  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.83,0:21:58.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What are you doing, SpongeBob?
Dialogue: 1,0:21:58.40,0:22:00.79,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,章鱼哥  你回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.40,0:22:00.79,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Squidward, you're back
Dialogue: 1,0:22:01.09,0:22:03.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,咒语生效了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.09,0:22:03.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The magic words worked
Dialogue: 1,0:22:03.12,0:22:05.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我原来真的有法力
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.12,0:22:05.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I really am magic after all
Dialogue: 1,0:22:05.72,0:22:07.34,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我能把你变成别的东西了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.72,0:22:07.34,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Can I turn you into something else now?
Dialogue: 1,0:22:08.95,0:22:09.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,停车
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.95,0:22:09.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Stop
Dialogue: 1,0:22:11.19,0:22:12.24,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,快带我走
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.19,0:22:12.24,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Get me out of here
Dialogue: 1,0:22:14.89,0:22:15.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.89,0:22:15.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hey, SpongeBob?
Dialogue: 1,0:22:16.32,0:22:17.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我还是很饿
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.32,0:22:17.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm still hungry
Dialogue: 1,0:22:17.40,0:22:19.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,能把我变成一罐蛋黄酱
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.40,0:22:19.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Will you turn me into a jar of mayonnaise
Dialogue: 1,0:22:19.46,0:22:20.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,让我自己吃自己吗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.46,0:22:20.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,so I can eat myself?
Dialogue: 1,0:22:21.52,0:22:22.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好啊  兄弟
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.52,0:22:22.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sure, buddy
Dialogue: 1,0:22:22.41,0:22:24.99,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,派大星变蛋黄酱
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.41,0:22:24.99,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Patrick-ah, mayonnaise-ica
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.94,0:22:28.82,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(712,806)}蛋黄酱
